      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I think it would be nice to have an RPC to fill a blank descriptor wallet with specific descriptor types instead of the all-or-blank approach right now.\r\n\r\nHaven't thought a lot about not providing legacy/p2sh by default for non-blank wallets, but there are still some places that refuse to upgrade and can only support payout to base58 addresses.",
