      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "I agree with removing legacy by default (and argued for that [here](https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gui/pull/459#issuecomment-961328134), but the legacy address option was added back to the GUI in this PR: https://github.com/bitcoin-core/gui/pull/459.\r\n\r\nAccording to https://en.bitcoin.it/wiki/Bech32_adoption almost everyone can now send to Bech32.  Doing this will probably help with the last stragglers.",
